#          https://github.com/xxjwxc/gormt/blob/master/go.mod
# Manpage: No traditional manpage; documentation in
#          repo README.md + README_zh_cn.md.
# Library: gorm.io/gorm (Jinzhu Zhang's "fantastic ORM
#          library for Golang" — the headline dependency
#          for this completion's axis-companion role;
#          see taxonomy notes below).  Also spf13/cobra
#          (Axis 1 argparse), gorm.io/driver/mysql
#          (gorm MySQL driver), jroimartin/gocui
#          (terminal UI), go-playground/validator.v9
#          (input validation), nicksnyder/go-i18n
#          (i18n localization), gopkg.in/yaml.v3 (Axis
#          20 YAML covered).
